{"tid":467286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【斧頭幫再現】沙頭角5匪攜斧截車打劫 搶$300萬火燒車","createTime":"2017-11-13T11:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T12:35:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"84c4633dc3514585fe28650182e357724fe100a9","tid":467286,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510562854_b58d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510562854_b58d.jpg&h=6f655575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙頭角發生劫案，下午4時許，一班劫匪乘私家車於沙頭角公路禾坑段截停另一部車，據報至少4名男子持斧頭落車，扑爆對方的車窗後，劫去車上約300萬元現金，得手即後乘車逃去。警方接報展開「捷進行動」追截賊車。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，賊車逃避警方追截時，於沙頭角公路萬屋邊疑失控撞向對面線另一部車，其中一部車碰撞後隨即冒煙起火。受事件影響，上址交通嚴重擠塞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171113/57453472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57453472&d=FydGCMgBuTxKnhUi7BncYZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=85e38059\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57453472&h=4ae510b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171113/57453472</a>"},{"pid":"a73483e0e435e93da1034199905e1d185d4c5b60","tid":467286,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510562854_b58d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510562854_b58d.jpg&h=6f655575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙頭角發生劫案，下午4時許，一班劫匪乘私家車於沙頭角公路禾坑段截停另一部車，據報至少4名男子持斧頭落車，扑爆對方的車窗後，劫去車上約300萬元現金，得手即後乘車逃去。警方接報展開「捷進行動」追截賊車。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，賊車逃避警方追截時，於沙頭角公路萬屋邊疑失控撞向對面線另一部車，其中一部